location.fullValue: Dunlap Plan, Bowes Creek Country Club - The Fairways Collection

data.description: Wonderful Millbrook model with First Floor Primary Suite in Bowes Creek 55+ Country Club Community.  Perfect for entertaining with a large open floor plan. From the Formal Dining Room, move into the Gourmet Kitchen offering a huge L-shaped wall of cabinets, both upper and lower, Corian countertops, pantry cabinet, stainless steel appliances and an island with sink and prep area. The casual dining area overlooks a huge Great Room with vaulted ceilings and a view of the second floor loft. A wall of windows lets in loads of natural light and features an atrium door to the back porch for relaxing evenings.  The large Primary Suite offers a walk-in closet and a luxury bath that features a soaking tub, separate shower and dual vanity. A second full bedroom/den has access to the second full bath. There is a service hall to the 2+car garage and first floor utility/laundry room with utility sink and cabinets.  The second level has a huge loft/family room plus a guest suite with bedroom, full bath and separate sitting area. There is also a giant walk in closet that's perfect for all those extra storage items like Holiday decor! Bowes Creek Country Club offers a clubhouse, restaurant, golf course, pool, walking trails and parks all located just minutes from Randall Road shopping district, I-90 and Metra station.
